reviewText: I pretty good DVD, the first dvd is when Madonna talks about her rebel hearts tour, and other interviews about her mdna tour, the second dvd is the I'm sexy DVD, which is others talking about Madonna
A very nice set of three DVDs about Madonna. All the DVDs were very good and the interviews with the girl herself were really interesting. A great set for fans of this talented lady

This set is very good VFM with 3 x DVDs included, all of which I found interesting and informative - as another reviewer mentions,, one of the films is a collection of interviews with the girl herself, and this has some really good clips included that I wasn't aware of - and shows a side of Madonna that was quite unexpected and unknown to me. The other two films are documentaries looking at different angles of her career and life and both are worth watching
